<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bohol HEIRLOOM SEED KEEPER</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --forest-green: #2d4a22;
            --mint-green: #416d33;
            --soil-brown: #2c1a11;
            --terracotta: #b85a38;
            --sand-beige: #dcc48e;
            --light-bg: #f4eee1;
            --code-bg: #1e1e1e;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            color: var(--soil-brown);
            line-height: 1.6;
            /* Earthy organic background patterning */
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(var(--sand-beige) 1px, transparent 0),
                radial-gradient(var(--sand-beige) 1px, transparent 0);
            background-size: 24px 24px;
            background-position: 0 0, 12px 12px;
        }

        /* Top Header Brand Bar */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--soil-brown), var(--forest-green));
            color: white;
            padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 6px solid var(--sand-beige);
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .header-logo {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        header h1 span {
            color: var(--sand-beige);
        }

        header p.tagline {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #e2ecd7;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        /* Secondary Navigation / Status Bar */
        .nav-bar {
            background-color: var(--sand-beige);
            color: var(--soil-brown);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .nav-bar span {
            margin: 0 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .nav-bar .separator {
            color: var(--terracotta);
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        /* Main Workspace Container */
        .workspace {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Split-screen Dashboard Framework mimicking the uploaded design layout */
        .dashboard-layout {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background: var(--soil-brown);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        @media (min-width: 900px) {
            .dashboard-layout {
                flex-direction: row;
            }
        }

        /* Left Side: Mock Interactive Code Panel */
        .code-panel {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: var(--code-bg);
            padding: 2rem;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #d4d4d4;
            overflow-x: auto;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--forest-green);
        }

        @media (min-width: 900px) {
            .code-panel {
                border-bottom: none;
                border-right: 2px solid var(--forest-green);
            }
        }

        .code-header {
            color: #85c1e9;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .json-key { color: #9cdcfe; }
        .json-val { color: #ce9178; }
        .json-string { color: #b5cea8; }
        .json-bracket { color: #ffd700; }

        /* Right Side: Beautiful Interactive Details Panel */
        .details-panel {
            flex: 1.2;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #3a2518, #23140e);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            color: #f4eee1;
        }

        .panel-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--sand-beige);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(220, 196, 142, 0.2);
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Pillars Grid Layout */
        .pillars-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 600px) {
            .pillars-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        /* Pillar Cards inspired explicitly by the brown/orange/green tiles in user image */
        .pillar-card {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .pillar-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .card-sovereignty { background-color: #a04d30; color: #ffffff; } /* Terracotta */
        .card-resilience { background-color: #bc9853; color: #2c1a11; }  /* Ochre/Sand */
        .card-innovation { background-color: #385e30; color: #ffffff; }  /* Forest Green */
        .card-heritage { background-color: #cca45c; color: #2c1a11; }    /* Gold/Beige */

        .pillar-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .pillar-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* Vision & Mission Highlight Row */
        .manifesto-section {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .manifesto-block {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .manifesto-block:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .manifesto-block h4 {
            color: var(--mint-green);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .manifesto-block p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #4a3b32;
        }

        /* Earthy Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--forest-green);
            color: #e2ecd7;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 5rem;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--terracotta);
        }

        footer .branding {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header>
        <div class="header-logo">🌱</div>
        <h1>BOHOL <span>HEIRLOOM SEED KEEPER</span></h1>
        <p class="tagline">Seed Sovereignty Initiative</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Nav Bar Status Bar -->
    <div class="nav-bar">
        <span>GREEN GARDENS OF HOPE</span>
        <span class="separator">|</span>
        <span>NETWORK</span>
        <span class="separator">|</span>
        <span>MAP</span>
        <span class="separator">|</span>
        <span>LIBRARY</span>
        <span class="separator">|</span>
        <span>CONTACT</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Context -->
    <div class="workspace">
        
        <div class="dashboard-layout">
            
            <!-- Left Side: Interactive Code Block -->
            <div class="code-panel">
                <div class="code-header">
                    <span>⚙️ config.json</span>
                    <span>JSON</span>
                </div>
                <span class="json-bracket">{</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-key">"initiative"</span>: <span class="json-val">"Bohol Heirloom Seed Keeper"</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-key">"innovator"</span>: <span class="json-val">"Green Gardens of Hope Agriventures Inc."</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-key">"location"</span>: <span class="json-val">"Bohol, Philippines"</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-key">"purpose"</span>: <span class="json-val">"Preservation & Ethical Seed Distribution"</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-key">"core_pillars"</span>: <span class="json-bracket">[</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-val">"Seed Sovereignty"</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-val">"Climate Resilience"</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-val">"Circular Agro-Innovation"</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-val">"Heritage Preservation"</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-bracket">]</span>,<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="json-key">"status"</span>: <span class="json-val">"Active / Community-Led"</span><br>
                <span class="json-bracket">}</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Side: Graphic Pillar Overview -->
            <div class="details-panel">
                <div class="panel-title">Project Details</div>
                
                <div class="pillars-grid">
                    <!-- Seed Sovereignty -->
                    <div class="pillar-card card-sovereignty">
                        <h3>🌾 Seed Sovereignty</h3>
                        <p>Empowering farming families to save, adapt, breed, and freely share open-pollinated heirloom varieties without industrial corporate strings.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Climate Resilience -->
                    <div class="pillar-card card-resilience">
                        <h3>☀️ Climate Resilience</h3>
                        <p>Multiplying ancestral crops with long-standing natural genetic resistance to local climate shifts, indigenous pests, and soil variations.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Circular Agro-Innovation -->
                    <div class="pillar-card card-innovation">
                        <h3>🔄 Circular Innovation</h3>
                        <p>Merging passed-down wisdom with highly optimized, modern zero-waste substrates and closed-loop local systems for self-reliance.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Heritage Preservation -->
                    <div class="pillar-card card-heritage">
                        <h3>🏛️ Heritage Preservation</h3>
                        <p>Protecting the traditional ecological stories, farming practices, and identity inherited from generations of Boholano agricultural families.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision and Mission Section -->
        <div class="manifesto-section">
            <div class="manifesto-block">
                <h4>👁️ Our Vision</h4>
                <p>To see Bohol thrive as a vibrant sanctuary of seed sovereignty and climate-smart agriculture, where food security is permanently rooted in biodiverse, community-owned ancestral soil.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="manifesto-block" style="margin-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1.5rem;">
                <h4>🎯 Our Mission</h4>
                <p>To systematically identify, preserve, and multiply native open-pollinated heirloom seeds across Bohol through community-driven seed libraries, circular agro-innovations, and the empowerment of local farmers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Website Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="branding">Green Gardens of Hope Agriventures Inc.</div>
        <p>Bohol Philippines Heirloom Seed Network (BHSN) Initiative</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.75rem;">&copy; 2026. All Rights Sovereign.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
